re_item_assets/steam/apps/1595710/extras/1eb7bb4ae5774a65c5af4e5fddd2e67a.avif?t=1760206532\" width=587 height=85 /></span><br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><strong>等级系统</strong></li></ul>在关卡系统中前进并解锁角色和新枪。<br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><strong>游戏多样性</strong></li></ul>每张地图都有自己的特点和机制。<br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><strong>疯狂模式</strong></li></ul>如果您正在寻找挑战，疯狂模式就是为您而设的。 更快，更难，更疯狂！<br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><strong>免费重大更新</strong></li></ul>被黑暗追赶会定期更新免费内容。 新地图、各种敌人和新玩法。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1595710/extras/23e26a379997c8004870bec79b042f61.poster.avif?t=1760206532\" width=600 height=214 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1595710/extras/23e26a379997c8004870bec79b042f61.webm?t=1760206532\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1595710/extras/23e26a379997c8004870bec79b042f61.mp4?t=1760206532\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >警告</h2>此游戏包含闪光灯，可能不适合患有光敏性癫痫或其他光敏状况的人使用。 建议玩家酌情决定。",
